{
  "stem": "7739.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I think I missed telling you what happened to my brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My brother had gone to these Christian people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As the expulsion was taking place, he came-- he came to the market square.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know he wasn't stupid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was smart enough to realize that he was supposed to stay with these Christian people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came, and of course, he was expelled with everybody else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother's work permit wasn't honored, and nor was my sister's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my sister, my mother, and my younger brother, together with the whole of the Jewish population, was done away with at that particular day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father, my older brother, myself-- because we were encamped in this forced labor camp-- and we stayed there under terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The first few days, when I run back to the column after these Ukrainian guards were searching me, my father went to work and I was assigned a barrack.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember just like now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the bunks were so shallow that if you slipped in on your stomach, you couldn't turn around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You had to come out and go in on your back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was there for about three days, crying, until my father finally found me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And what happened when he found me is, I-- the bunks were bedded out with sawdust.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no straw like for mattresses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was boards with sawdust.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He took me out of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He says, you come and join me in my barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I says, well, before we go in your barrack, I says, I got lots of sawdust in my shirt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I shake it out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I took off my shirt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
